author: _cointel
description: We Made The Zoot Suit of the Decade. For the past few months, we‚Äôve been building something special. Spike Lee wanted to channel ‚ÄúShorty‚Äù, his iconic character from Malcolm X and reintroduce him to the world, this time with the wisdom, vision, and fire of 2025. We took that challenge personally. What followed was a journey through sketches, fittings, setbacks, breakthroughs, and above all craftsmanship. Every inch of this suit was drafted from scratch. We custom dyed grosgrain for each stripe, hand-cut every panel, sourced gold buttons to echo Harlem Renaissance elegance, and built the silhouette from a muslin draft to final fitting. It wasn‚Äôt just a suit. It was a resurrection. A cultural blueprint. A modern revival of the unapologetic flair of 1940s zoot suits, reimagined through a contemporary Black lens. And we believe, we made the zoot suit of the decade. This was made with no factory. Just vision, grit, and trust. Design and creative direction by COINTEL. Thank you, Spike, for trusting us to dress the moment. This is only the beginning. #COINTEL #ZootSuitOfTheDecade #SpikeLee #Cannes2025
